<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.240310>
    dc:description "FIGURE 89. Egonpretneria vudutschajldi sp. n., paratype male from the Rođakuša Pit, Velebit Mt., labral teeth. Scale line: 0.3 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/240310/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.240294>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 8. Egonpretneria vudutschajldi sp. n., paratype male from the Rođakuša Pit, Velebit Mt. 1: body segments XV and XVI, dorsal view; 2: body segment XV, dorsal view; 3: body segment XVI, dorsal view; 4: limbus of body segment XVI; 5: cross-section of body segment XVI, posterior view; 6: external macrochaetae of body segment XVI; 7: metazonal warts of body segment XVI; 8: body segments XV and XVI, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/240294/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.240296>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15 – 18. Egonpretneria vudutschajldi sp. n., paratype male from the Rođakuša Pit, Velebit Mt., gonopods. 15: anterior gonopods, anterior view; 16: anterior gonopods, posterior view; 17: anterior gonopods, lateral view; 18: posterior gonopods, anterior view. Designations: a: anterior shield-like coxal process, b: bristles apparatus, d: subapical latero-caudal denticle, l: lamella, m: uniramous medial sternal process, v: posterior medial vesicle, lp: lateral process, pp: posterior process, lcp: lateral coxal process, sco: syncoxal rounded lobe. Scale line: 0.3 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/240296/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

